Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.20,0:00:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,（洛杉磯西元2029年）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.13,0:01:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,（那些機器從核子戰火中崛起）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.77,0:01:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,（它們滅絕人類的戰爭肆虐數十年）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.28,0:01:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,（但最後的一場仗不會在未來掀起）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.82,0:01:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,（它會發生在這裡，就是現在）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.86,0:01:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,（就在今晚）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.67,0:03:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,片名：魔鬼終結者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.81,0:03:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,（洛杉磯1984年早上1點52分）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.11,0:04:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.38,0:04:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他媽的……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.62,0:04:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.58,0:05:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，輪到我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.10,0:05:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.94,0:05:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個人搞什麼鬼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.71,0:05:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夜色很好，適宜散步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.22,0:05:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天是洗衣日，沒乾淨衣服穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.56,0:05:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.80,0:05:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對，沒乾淨衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.40,0:06:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個傢伙一定是喝醉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.61,0:06:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.98,0:06:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.45,0:06:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去你的，混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.02,0:06:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿，甜心，怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.47,0:06:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不必忍受那個的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.47,0:06:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她老是纏著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.63,0:07:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兄弟，你有沒有見到一道強光？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.64,0:07:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到那傢伙嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.08,0:08:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.61,0:08:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在逃跑，別動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.28,0:08:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.03,0:08:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個混蛋……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.56,0:08:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搶了我的褲子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.80,0:08:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天是什麼日子？日期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.64,0:08:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5月12號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.01,0:08:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,星期四，什麼年份？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.64,0:08:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.21,0:09:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他搶了我的槍，快追
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.04,0:11:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(莎拉康納）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.18,0:12:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大塊頭，替我守著它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.40,0:12:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好，我遲到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.33,0:12:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.60,0:12:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(莎拉康納）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.74,0:13:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開工了，我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.66,0:13:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻煩你拿咖啡給我，好嗎？—好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.57,0:13:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牛排是誰的？我叫了烤牛肉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.27,0:13:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有薯條，他要牛肉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.24,0:13:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫的是辣牛肉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.71,0:13:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰點的牛排？ -小姐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.45,0:13:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們想點菜，好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.36,0:13:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.99,0:13:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.54,0:13:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是真皮吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.19,0:13:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孩子，做得好，我該把小費給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.26,0:13:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要這樣想，一百年後誰會在乎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.03,0:13:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(阿萊姆體育用品槍械店）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.09,0:13:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那支12口徑自動步槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.81,0:13:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,義大利製造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.48,0:14:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以選手動或自動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.45,0:14:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,點45口徑滑動式配紅外線瞄準器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.52,0:14:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它們是全新的，才剛收到是支好槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.73,0:14:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紅外線亮起時 你把紅點對準目標就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.34,0:14:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,百發百中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.41,0:14:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有什麼需要？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.31,0:14:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一支40瓦的同步等離子步槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.98,0:14:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是你看到的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.86,0:14:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那支烏茲型九毫米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.73,0:14:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你很熟識槍械 任何一支都適合家居防衛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.62,0:14:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.42,0:14:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要哪一支呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.85,0:14:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.86,0:14:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天可以提早關門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.47,0:14:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手槍要等15天，但你現在可拿走那些步槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.91,0:14:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不能這樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.18,0:14:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.97,0:15:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好，寶貝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.48,0:15:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.99,0:15:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要你來接我，我的摩托車壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.12,0:15:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不管，來接我，什麼……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.20,0:15:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫特？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.57,0:15:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的態度很有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.19,0:15:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫特，你在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.62,0:15:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別這樣，你在幹什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.49,0:15:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(莎拉康納……）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.53,0:16:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎拉康納？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.97,0:16:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.70,0:16:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在休息，卡拉代替我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.21,0:16:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎拉，過來，這算是跟你有關的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.09,0:16:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可思議，你不會相信的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.43,0:16:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐下，你會喜歡這個的—什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.23,0:16:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有幾個目擊證人指出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.94,0:16:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一位莎拉康納35歲，有兩名子女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.22,0:16:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天下午在家裡中槍身亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.79,0:17:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.84,0:20:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你喜歡音響，最佳的音響……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.17,0:20:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是鮑博身歷聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.89,0:20:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們有低音喇叭、高頻喇叭數位揚聲器和鐳射唱片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.79,0:20:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有圖表等化器和音響平衡器……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.59,0:20:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.38,0:21:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.09,0:21:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先，我會一個個的解開你的鈕扣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.43,0:21:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後用我的舌頭從你的頭舔到你赤裸的乳房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.01,0:21:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後，慢慢地……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.58,0:21:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逐一地脫掉你的牛仔褲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.19,0:21:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,金珍，是麥特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.70,0:21:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後打圈地舔你的肚皮……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.03,0:21:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再往下面去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.03,0:21:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後用牙齒……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.81,0:21:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,脫掉你的內褲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.38,0:21:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.18,0:21:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天啊，莎拉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.33,0:21:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的天，對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.53,0:21:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以為你是……我想找金珍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.64,0:21:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的，老友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.28,0:21:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那個變態鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.40,0:21:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先，我會一個個解開你的鈕扣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.00,0:22:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冷靜點－你們這班混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.57,0:22:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等著我對付你們，放手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.35,0:22:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.62,0:22:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.07,0:22:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有什麼？女性受害者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.37,0:22:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.87,0:22:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎拉康納，秘書，35歲在不足十尺內身中六槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.58,0:22:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大口徑的武器—我看得清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.52,0:22:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼？第二名女死者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.42,0:22:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天下午山谷區分區送過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.81,0:22:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我肯定這些命案是有動機的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.64,0:22:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看看死者的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.26,0:22:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎拉……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.96,0:22:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,康……有沒有弄錯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.90,0:22:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說笑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.21,0:22:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,報紙會大做文章的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.94,0:22:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個在一天內有特定模式的兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.88,0:22:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我討厭古怪的案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.76,0:22:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.91,0:22:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比凡人得到的更好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.76,0:23:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有沒有見過寶斯利？—最近沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.50,0:23:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你聽了留言沒有？—我以為你聽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.88,0:23:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎拉，是媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.99,0:23:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來你在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.96,0:23:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想想你媽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.93,0:23:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.38,0:23:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好，莎拉，史丹莫斯基
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.18,0:23:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有突發事件令我不能應約了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.88,0:23:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能丟下不理的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.46,0:23:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，我會給你賠罪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.46,0:23:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,改天找你吧，對不起，再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.45,0:23:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個混蛋，有輛保時捷又怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.32,0:23:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不能這樣對待你的 這是週五晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.26,0:23:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.00,0:23:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會打爆他的膝蓋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.07,0:23:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寶斯利仍然愛我，是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.32,0:24:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天，真噁心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.89,0:24:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去看電影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.40,0:24:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和麥特玩得開心點—我們會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.77,0:24:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也是－好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.72,0:24:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該死，麥特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:13.28,0:25:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:15.46,0:25:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們可有發現那些命案是依電話薄裡的次序發生的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:20.00,0:25:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以說什麼？無可奉告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:22.18,0:25:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是發生了兩宗命案……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:35.40,0:25:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那杯咖啡早就涼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:38.75,0:25:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還用它弄熄香煙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:41.78,0:25:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能找到下一名女子嗎？—我不斷聽到電話留言……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:45.50,0:25:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派一組人去—已經派了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:46.93,0:25:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有回音，那個經理還沒有回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:49.23,0:25:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打電話給她—剛打了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:51.73,0:25:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再找她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:53.48,0:25:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我一支香煙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:05.30,0:26:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:07.27,0:26:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄到你了，你在跟答錄機談話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:10.22,0:26:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但別害羞，答錄機也需要愛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:12.62,0:26:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟它談談吧，金珍，就是我……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:15.80,0:26:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或者莎拉會回復你的，等候訊號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:20.37,0:26:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又是一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:23.37,0:26:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在聽到了就叫他做‘電話薄殺手’吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:27.45,0:26:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我討厭這些報界觸目的案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:30.19,0:26:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特別是變態的觸目案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:33.87,0:26:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:35.57,0:26:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發表聲明，叫這班走狗替我們工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:39.32,0:26:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若我可以在11點前上電視……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:41.69,0:26:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或者她會找我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:44.06,0:26:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:45.63,0:26:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的樣子怎樣？—很難看，老總
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:48.50,0:26:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:51.27,0:26:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛收到消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:52.48,0:26:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警方已經宣佈了第二名死者的姓名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:56.66,0:26:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是今天發生的命案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:59.19,0:27:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很奇怪，兩名死者都是同名同姓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:02.77,0:27:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩小時前，35歲的莎拉康納……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:05.44,0:27:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被發現死在寓所裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:08.01,0:27:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,轉台吧－莎拉康納……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:10.42,0:27:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別碰它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:11.96,0:27:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在她家中被殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:14.23,0:27:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警方拒絕猜測……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:16.46,0:27:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩宗案件的類似之處……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:18.37,0:27:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在仍未發現兩者之間有何關連
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:23.05,0:27:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們會隨時為大家報導最新消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:48.31,0:27:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(莎拉康納……）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:53.99,0:28:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(黑科技酒吧）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:57.74,0:28:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有電話嗎？在裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:00.01,0:29:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四塊半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:41.83,0:29:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你已接通洛杉磯警局緊急熱線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:45.14,0:29:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的線路忙碌中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:46.61,0:29:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果需召警車支援，請稍候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:50.18,0:29:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在第三街與奧林匹克街交界的鮑勃酒鋪附近有狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:54.37,0:30:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:56.37,0:30:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會拿你來制皮帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:13.28,0:31:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別逼我打你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:15.62,0:32:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:17.35,0:32:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄到你了，你在跟答錄機談話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:19.60,0:32:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但別害羞，答錄機也需要愛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:22.83,0:32:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟它談談吧……金珍，就是我……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:25.31,0:32:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或者莎拉會回覆你的，等候訊號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:29.85,0:32:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,金珍，是莎拉，快接聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:32.05,0:32:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在比科大道的黑科技酒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:36.10,0:32:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:38.07,0:32:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人跟蹤我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:41.38,0:32:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望你快點聽這個留言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:43.55,0:32:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想你來接我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:46.79,0:32:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警方不停轉接我的電話線我會再試的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:50.37,0:32:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡的號碼是5559175
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:54.74,0:32:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快找我，我要你幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:11.39,0:33:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(莎拉康納）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:13.99,0:33:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:16.29,0:33:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎拉康納？我是特斯勒警長—聽著……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:19.74,0:33:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別要我等或者轉線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:22.24,0:33:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會，你在哪裡？一間叫黑科技的酒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:26.69,0:33:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道，在比科大道你沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:29.69,0:33:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事，但我覺得有人在跟蹤我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:33.06,0:33:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留心聽著，你身處公眾地方會較安全的，我們會儘快來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:37.54,0:33:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留在原地，別出去，別上廁所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:40.55,0:33:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會很快派一輛車來—好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:05.82,0:34:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個傢伙沒有付錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:48.84,0:36:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想活著就跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:59.49,0:37:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:14.13,0:38:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是1—L19，有人襲擊後逃跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:16.84,0:38:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可疑車輛是舊型灰色福特在第七街向西逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:21.25,0:38:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他開得很快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:23.49,0:38:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上派救護車來第七街和百老匯街交界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:29.03,0:38:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:34.45,0:38:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有單位留意一輛舊型灰色福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:37.15,0:38:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後被發現在第七街和百老匯街交界，向西行走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:47.11,0:38:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐穩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:59.54,0:39:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有沒有受傷？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:02.01,0:39:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有沒有中槍？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:09.29,0:39:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照我的話做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:10.96,0:39:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照著做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:12.90,0:39:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:14.54,0:39:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要發出聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:16.61,0:39:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:18.81,0:39:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白嗎？－明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:20.82,0:39:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求你別傷害我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:40.70,0:39:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是來幫你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:42.64,0:39:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我姓萊斯，科技部隊中士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:44.74,0:39:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,DN38416，受命來保護你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:47.48,0:39:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是被毀滅的目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:54.66,0:39:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嫌疑犯在國家街和奧林匹克街交界1—L19，請通話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:59.18,0:40:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是1—L19，在奧林匹克街向西行接近奧佛蘭道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:08.06,0:40:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是搞錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:10.50,0:40:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒做過什麼－不，你會做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:13.64,0:40:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你保住性命是很重要的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:15.88,0:40:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是真的那個人怎能站起來追你……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:19.48,0:40:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它不是人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:20.92,0:40:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是機器，一個終結者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:23.43,0:40:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,電腦達因系統101型號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:34.22,0:40:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機器？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:36.63,0:40:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像機械人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:38.33,0:40:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是機械人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:40.10,0:40:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是電子人，電腦控制的生物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:43.00,0:40:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，他剛才在流血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:44.82,0:40:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:48.95,0:40:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趴下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:35.13,0:41:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，聽著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:36.59,0:41:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,魔鬼終結者是個混合體半人半機械
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:40.21,0:41:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裡面是一個超合金的戰鬥骨架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:43.31,0:41:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由微型處理器操作，全副武裝，非常強勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:47.39,0:41:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但外表是活人組織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:49.83,0:41:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肌肉、皮膚、毛髮、血液都是為電子人培植的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:54.51,0:41:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想我怎樣做？—留心聽著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:56.94,0:41:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要丟掉這輛車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:04.16,0:42:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,600系列有塑膠皮膚很容易認得出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:08.37,0:42:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但這批是新造的，它們很像人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:10.91,0:42:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流汗、口臭，諸如此類很難辨認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:14.98,0:42:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要等他向你下手才可以對付他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:18.56,0:42:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽著……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:20.23,0:42:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是蠢才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:22.37,0:42:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們還不能製造那樣的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:24.51,0:42:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:26.58,0:42:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,40年後就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:30.99,0:42:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是說它來自未來？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:33.46,0:42:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個有可能的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:36.23,0:42:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從你的角度看我對科技一竅不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:40.51,0:42:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼你也是來自未來？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:43.02,0:42:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:43.98,0:42:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:53.14,0:42:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,電子人感覺不到痛楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:55.58,0:42:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我感覺得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:57.25,0:42:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要再那樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:59.12,0:43:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放我走－聽著……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:01.49,0:43:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有搞清楚點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:02.90,0:43:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個毀滅者就在外面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:06.80,0:43:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它是沒情可講的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:08.74,0:43:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不講道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:11.29,0:43:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它不會感到可惜或後悔……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:14.26,0:43:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或者恐懼，它絕不會甘休
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:18.14,0:43:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,永遠不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:19.87,0:43:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直到你死掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:31.59,0:43:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可否制止它？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:37.51,0:43:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:40.88,0:43:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠這些武器，我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:59.86,0:44:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有單位，灰色福特……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:01.73,0:44:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在一個停車場裡發現可疑車輛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:04.41,0:44:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地點是第四街和百老匯街交界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:10.88,0:44:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,位置是下層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:15.96,0:44:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,疑匪是個年約25歲，身高六尺穿綠色外衣的白種男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:20.28,0:44:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後被發現在……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:47.97,0:44:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萊斯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:50.01,0:44:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何是我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:54.22,0:44:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它為何要對付我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:02.37,0:45:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,曾經發生了一場核戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:06.22,0:45:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,未來數年後……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:10.99,0:45:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡的一切……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:13.39,0:45:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個地方，所有的東西……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:16.80,0:45:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都會消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:20.11,0:45:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就此消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:22.25,0:45:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一些生還者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:24.39,0:45:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,零星的……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:25.86,0:45:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,散落各地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:29.00,0:45:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有人知道是誰發動戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:34.41,0:45:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那些機器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:37.52,0:45:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:39.29,0:45:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,防衛網路電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:42.49,0:45:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新型的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:44.54,0:45:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,功能強勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:46.87,0:45:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接駁到所有的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:48.68,0:45:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被委託操控一切的重任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:51.69,0:45:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們說它變得聰明起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:54.29,0:45:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一種智慧的新秩序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:57.63,0:46:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它視所有人類為威脅不能與我們共存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:03.11,0:46:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它在那間決定了我們的命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:07.09,0:46:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滅絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:23.76,0:46:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可有目睹這場戰爭？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:37.56,0:46:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:39.40,0:46:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在戰後長大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:41.26,0:46:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在廢墟中成長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:42.83,0:46:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,挨饑抵餓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:44.30,0:46:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,躲避那些HK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:46.08,0:46:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,HK？追捕殺手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:48.95,0:46:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機械工廠製造的巡邏機器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:53.00,0:46:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們大部分人被圍捕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:54.67,0:46:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關在營裡等候被逐一消滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:58.50,0:47:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是被雷射掃瞄器烙下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:05.02,0:47:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們有部分人得以活下來……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:07.56,0:47:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,負責……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:10.47,0:47:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搬運屍體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:13.14,0:47:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些消滅單位日以繼夜地運作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:15.84,0:47:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們差點就喪命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:22.16,0:47:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但有一個人……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:25.17,0:47:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,教我們反抗，衝擊監禁營的線路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:27.94,0:47:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把那些金屬混蛋撞個稀巴爛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:32.85,0:47:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他扭轉了局勢，帶我們脫離險境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:36.09,0:47:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他姓康納
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:38.80,0:47:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,約翰康納
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:40.57,0:47:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:43.07,0:47:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你未出生的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:34.50,0:49:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你來開車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:42.72,0:49:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萊斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:03.93,0:50:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，萊斯，不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:05.97,0:50:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，他們會殺死你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:07.87,0:50:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在凱迪拉克車裡的人立刻舉高雙手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:13.69,0:50:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:19.03,0:50:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跪下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:21.17,0:50:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:22.58,0:50:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跪下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:27.61,0:50:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有PC—207單位注意疑匪已被制伏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:30.76,0:50:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,取消進一步支援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:52.55,0:50:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎拉……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:54.25,0:50:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喝一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:59.53,0:51:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你肯定是他們？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:01.60,0:51:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我應該看看屍體的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:04.57,0:51:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經證實了他們的身份沒有錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:07.45,0:51:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:11.25,0:51:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,金珍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:14.67,0:51:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小夥子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:16.43,0:51:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:18.87,0:51:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是西伯曼醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:20.60,0:51:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好，莎拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:21.94,0:51:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想你告訴他，萊斯對你說的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:24.72,0:51:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你應付得來嗎？—可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:29.87,0:51:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是個醫生？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:31.94,0:51:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犯罪學心理醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:34.10,0:51:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萊斯是不是瘋了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:35.91,0:51:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就是要查證一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:04.26,0:53:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是個軍人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:06.32,0:53:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保衛著誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:08.79,0:53:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隸屬第132團，由貝裡率領
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:12.17,0:53:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由21年到27年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:14.54,0:53:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:16.01,0:53:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,2027年？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:17.62,0:53:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:18.82,0:53:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後來我被派到……很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:22.09,0:53:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當約翰康納的部下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:23.66,0:53:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人是誰？一個電腦防衛系統……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:27.04,0:53:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該死，對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:29.44,0:53:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,電腦動力系統替薩諾力製造的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:32.96,0:53:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:34.96,0:53:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個電腦……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:36.33,0:53:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以為殺了敵人的母親就可以勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:41.18,0:53:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把他在孕育前就殺掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:44.45,0:53:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算是倒逆的墮胎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:48.06,0:53:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,西伯曼笑死我了\N那個傢伙把他弄得一頭霧水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:54.38,0:53:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不殺死約翰康納？\N為何要有這個毀滅者的計畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:58.46,0:53:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有選擇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:00.56,0:54:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它們的防禦網路被催毀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:03.04,0:54:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:04.47,0:54:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺掉約翰康納也不會有何分別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:07.48,0:54:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天網要剷除他整個組織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:10.45,0:54:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不是當你們操控了實驗室時找到的……那個什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:15.53,0:54:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時空轉移裝置？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:17.84,0:54:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:19.34,0:54:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個毀滅者已經穿越過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:22.05,0:54:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,康納派我來攔截它們把整個地方炸毀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:25.45,0:54:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎樣回去？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:27.36,0:54:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不可以回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:30.76,0:54:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有人可以回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:34.54,0:54:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有別人可以過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:37.35,0:54:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有他……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:39.38,0:54:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:25.46,0:56:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有他……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:27.13,0:56:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:30.71,0:56:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何你沒有帶武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:33.85,0:56:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一些更先進的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:36.43,0:56:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們沒有鐳射槍的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:39.23,0:56:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鐳射槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:40.80,0:56:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我看看一件未來的科技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:43.27,0:56:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要光著身體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:44.84,0:56:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它跟由生物產生的磁場有關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:48.05,0:56:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死物是不行的—為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:50.08,0:56:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那鬼東西不是我製造的—好的……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:53.26,0:56:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但這個電子人，若它是金屬的……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:56.50,0:56:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被活組織包著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:58.17,0:56:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對，是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:59.91,0:57:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可真有看頭我可以因他功成名就
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:03.12,0:57:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看這個多聰明？不需要證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:06.32,0:57:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大部分神經病幻覺都很複雜但這個卻很精明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:10.13,0:57:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何另外那兩個女人會被殺？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:13.00,0:57:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大部分記錄都在戰爭中遺失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:15.75,0:57:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天網對康納的母親幾乎一無所知她的全名……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:19.72,0:57:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她住在哪裡他們只知道在哪個城市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:22.32,0:57:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個毀滅者只是受系統操控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:24.73,0:57:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們再談談……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:26.44,0:57:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你聽夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:28.51,0:57:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經回答了你的問題現在我要見莎拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:31.75,0:57:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可不能作主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:33.65,0:57:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那為何我要跟你談？—因為……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:36.92,0:57:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰是主管？求你……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:37.93,0:57:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:39.94,0:57:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還是不明白，對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:42.77,0:57:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他會找到她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:44.61,0:57:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他就是要那樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:46.32,0:57:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他只會那樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:48.25,0:57:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你制止不了他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:50.22,0:57:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他會宰了你，捏住她的喉嚨挖出她的心臟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:53.97,0:57:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:55.34,0:57:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:59.71,0:58:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:06.59,0:58:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萊斯是瘋了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:08.43,0:58:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用技術性的用語……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:10.64,0:58:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是個瘋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:12.41,0:58:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎拉，這是他們所謂的盔甲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:16.18,0:58:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的特種部隊都穿著這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:18.32,0:58:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能擋12口徑的火力那個人一定是穿了它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:23.06,0:58:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,觸摸一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:26.61,0:58:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打碎擋風玻璃又怎樣解釋？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:28.58,0:58:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他可能服食了麻醉藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:30.55,0:58:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若他折斷了手幾小時也感覺不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:33.63,0:58:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個傢伙……看見嗎？—拿著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:36.00,0:58:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:37.66,0:58:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡有一張沙發躺下來睡一會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:40.54,0:58:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你媽要一小時後才從大熊鎮抵達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:44.48,0:58:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我睡不著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:46.52,0:58:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,試試吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:47.86,0:58:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那張沙發其貌不揚，但很舒服的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:53.13,0:58:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你會絕對安全的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:55.78,0:58:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這座大廈裡有30個警員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:58.38,0:58:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:06.33,0:59:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚晚－晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:22.87,0:59:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是莎拉康納的朋友我知道她在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:26.48,0:59:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,—我可否見她？不可以，她在錄口供
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:29.45,0:59:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:31.05,0:59:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要一會兒的,你想等的話，那邊有張長椅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:45.59,0:59:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:14.16,1:00:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:25.45,1:00:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有槍聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:35.91,1:00:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不是恐怖分子？快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:42.89,1:00:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別走開
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:58.59,1:01:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們快離開這裡－來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:04.77,1:01:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點……
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:08.48,1:01:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看到他
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:24.48,1:01:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看著他
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:46.50,1:01:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自動式武器－快點，走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:16.94,1:02:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾特
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:33.78,1:02:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾特
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:04.05,1:03:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:07.12,1:03:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萊斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:12.03,1:03:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:53.64,1:03:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新聞時間，4點36分
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:56.34,1:03:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(燃料)
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:57.64,1:04:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主要新聞加州歷來最大型的……
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:00.44,1:04:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,執法行動正在展開
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:02.71,1:04:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五個南部縣區正在大舉搜捕……
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:09.93,1:04:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿著
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:14.44,1:04:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們把這個推離公路
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:48.25,1:04:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你冷嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:49.96,1:04:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凍僵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:05.02,1:05:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萊斯……
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:08.00,1:05:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有名字嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:10.37,1:05:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱優
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:12.04,1:05:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱優
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:14.11,1:05:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你穿越時空時是怎樣的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:18.89,1:05:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白光
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:23.60,1:05:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,痛楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:27.60,1:05:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許就像出生時一樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:29.62,1:05:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的天
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:32.45,1:05:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我剛才吃了一記
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:35.49,1:05:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你中槍了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:38.30,1:05:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是很嚴重
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:40.37,1:05:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們要找醫生-沒事的，算了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:44.22,1:05:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了？你瘋了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:47.55,1:05:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,脫下它
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:01.22,1:06:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:02.96,1:06:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它穿過了皮肉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:06.03,1:06:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這會使我作嘔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:08.50,1:06:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你跟我談話好嗎—談什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:11.71,1:06:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道，隨便說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:13.89,1:06:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,談談我的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:16.89,1:06:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他有我這麼高大
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:22.14,1:06:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他有你的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:27.54,1:06:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是怎樣的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:29.86,1:06:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你信任他
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:32.06,1:06:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他有一種力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:35.06,1:06:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我願意為約翰康納犧牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:41.51,1:06:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在至少知道給他取什麼名宇
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:43.95,1:06:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不知道他父親是誰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:46.83,1:06:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好讓我遇上他時不會叫他滾開
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:49.83,1:06:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,約翰從來沒有提起他
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:52.63,1:06:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道他在戰前死了—等一會
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:57.15,1:06:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:59.93,1:07:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不是約翰派你來的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:03.10,1:07:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我自願的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:05.53,1:07:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:08.14,1:07:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有機會認識傳奇人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:11.18,1:07:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎拉康納
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:13.88,1:07:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她教她的兒子抵抗……
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:16.66,1:07:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,組織
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:18.53,1:07:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備，從他小時就開始教導他
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:20.57,1:07:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當其他人還在戰前躲避時
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:26.45,1:07:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你用過去式說一些我還沒有做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:30.19,1:07:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的令我發瘋
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:36.30,1:07:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你肯定找對了人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:38.88,1:07:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肯定
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:41.12,1:07:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是吧，我像未來的母親？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:46.80,1:07:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我堅強嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:48.70,1:07:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有組織能力？我連讓自己收支平衡都不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:54.52,1:07:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有要求這個榮譽也不想要它
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:58.18,1:07:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:03.23,1:08:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你兒子要我告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:05.90,1:08:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他要我背熟它
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:08.44,1:08:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‘感謝你在黑暗年代的勇氣’
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:11.72,1:08:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‘你要面對的事我幫不到你只能說未來還未定案’
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:16.42,1:08:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‘你一定要比你想像中更堅強’
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:19.13,1:08:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‘你一定要活下去否則我永不會存在’
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:22.80,1:08:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:27.29,1:08:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包紮得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:30.36,1:08:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你喜歡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:32.53,1:08:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我的第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:38.01,1:08:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,睡一會吧，快天亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:44.99,1:08:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:56.75,1:08:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再跟我談一會
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:02.19,1:09:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,談什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:04.44,1:09:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告訴我你從哪裡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:09.31,1:09:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:12.42,1:09:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你白天躲藏起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:15.06,1:09:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但在晚上你可以到處活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:17.46,1:09:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你仍然要小心因為追捕投手會用紅外線
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:22.84,1:09:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但它們不是太聰明
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:26.08,1:09:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,約翰教我們對付它們的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:29.46,1:09:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是當那些滲透者出現的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:32.60,1:09:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毀滅者是最新型的……最難對付的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:45.73,1:09:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它正在以搜尋模式闖進你的防區
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:48.77,1:09:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在你以北750米的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:55.56,1:09:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:41.86,1:10:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萊斯，DN—384……
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:44.07,1:10:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對，讓他進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:54.19,1:10:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的監察者有一隻爪壞了所以要減少巡邏
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:58.56,1:11:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收到，揚基17，你可以安全折返
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:17.65,1:12:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毀滅者……
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:37.00,1:13:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我夢見一些狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:40.91,1:13:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們用它們來提防毀滅者
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:43.91,1:13:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的世界很可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:25.57,1:14:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老友，你裡面有只死貓嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:33.10,1:14:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(可能的回應：是，不是或走開）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:36.17,1:14:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,（去你的，混蛋）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:37.34,1:14:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去你的，混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:47.92,1:14:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(媽媽的小屋大熊鎮雲杉路181號)
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:58.19,1:14:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該死
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:00.49,1:15:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:03.72,1:15:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(迪基旅館)
